
Dungeon Crawl:
8-15 Minute Playtime

Essentially a classic Dungeon Crawler, 
Terrifying Dark Future, Character of Rot, Tin, and Flesh. 

Find Oneself in an Ancient Castle, with no Exit Doors. 
Fell through a hall of mirrors. 

Characters:
Wizard
Root Witch
Demon Cultist
Blood Tornado
Skeleton King
Blind Monk
Hopeless Knight

Items:
Xyzzy
Broomstick
Jagged Dagger
Bone Amulet
Goblet
Tattered Vestment

Find a wizard who gives the spell:
Xyzzy (allows for teleport) 
